      <title>新输油管道导致美国主要枢纽的石油储罐干涸</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/new-pipeline-has-oil-storage-tanks-at-key-us-hub-running-dry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于加拿大新建的一条大型管道将原油分流至其他地方，美国一个重要原油枢纽的储油罐已接近底部，这让交易商长期以来所依赖的市场信号变得混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/new-pipeline-has-oil-storage-tanks-at-key-us-hub-running-dry</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 15:15:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
